    "improvements_made": "Merged USER_PROFILE into USER to simplify the model and added soft‑delete (is_active) flags on USER, PRODUCT, CATEGORY, ADDRESS. Introduced PRODUCT_CATEGORY linking entity for a true many‑to‑many relationship between products and categories. Added ORDER_STATUS_HISTORY to capture full audit trail of order state changes. Created DISCOUNT and ORDER_DISCOUNT entities to support coupons, promotions, and price adjustments. Expanded LOG to record both admin and user actions with nullable admin_id/user_id and added ip_address for traceability. Included timestamps and active flags across entities for lifecycle management. Retained all previously strong components (order, order items, payment, shipment, address handling, admin audit)."
